\": 211, \"to\": 248}, {\"ngram\": \"around two laps\", \"from\": 282, \"to\": 297}, {\"ngram\": \"the Stade de France\", \"from\": 311, \"to\": 330}, {\"ngram\": \"her silver medal\", \"from\": 368, \"to\": 384}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Beatrice Chebet managed to steer clear of the trouble to claim gold with a time of 14:28:56, while Sifan Hassan's bronze was upgraded to a silver.\", \"from\": 387, \"to\": 533, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 387, \"end\": 402, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Beatrice_Chebet\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 0.0, \"text\": \"Beatrice Chebet\", \"types\": [\"Q729\", \"Q5\", \"Q215627\", \"Q19088\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Beatrice_Chebet\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Beatrice_Chebet\"}, {\"begin\": 486, \"end\": 498, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Sifan_Hassan\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 0.0, \"text\": \"Sifan Hassan\", \"types\": [\"Q729\", \"Q5\", \"Q215627\", \"Q19088\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Sifan_Hassan\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Sifan_Hassan\"}], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"the trouble\", \"from\": 429, \"to\": 440}, {\"ngram\": \"gold\", \"from\": 450, \"to\": 454}, {\"ngram\": \"a time\", \"from\": 460, \"to\": 466}, {\"ngram\": \"a silver\", \"from\": 524, \"to\": 532}]}, {\"sentence\": \"The Kenyan's disqualification also saw Nadia Battocletti of Italy promoted into the medal positions.\", \"from\": 534, \"to\": 634, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 573, \"end\": 590, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Nadia_Battocletti\", \"score\": 0.9999993194785517, \"rank\": 0.0, \"text\": \"Nadia Battocletti\", \"types\": [\"Q729\", \"Q5\", \"Q215627\", \"Q19088\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Nadia_Battocletti\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Nadia_Battocletti\"}, {\"begin\": 594, \"end\": 599, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Italy_national_football_team\", \"score\": 0.9999702562703285, \"rank\": 2.7674624934091102e-05, \"text\": \"Italy\", \"types\": [\"Q476028\", \"Q43229\", \"Q24229398\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Italy_national_football_team\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Italy_national_football_team\"}], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"The Kenyan's disqualification\", \"from\": 534, \"to\": 563}, {\"ngram\": \"the medal positions\", \"from\": 614, \"to\": 633}]}, {\"sentence\": \"However, in a stunning twist just hours later, Kipyegon was handed back the silver medal after Athletics Kenya lodged a successful appeal against the decision, meaning the bronze was returned to Hassan from Battocletti.\", \"from\": 636, \"to\": 855, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 731, \"end\": 746, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Athletics_Kenya\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 0.0, \"text\": \"Athletics Kenya\", \"types\": [], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Athletics_Kenya\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Athletics_Kenya\"}, {\"begin\": 831, \"end\": 837, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Prince_Hassan_bin_Talal\", \"score\": 0.7369344478807932, \"rank\": 0.3569575148556968, \"text\": \"Hassan\", \"types\": [\"Q729\", \"Q5\", \"Q215627\", \"Q19088\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Prince_Hassan_bin_Talal\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Prince_Hassan_bin_Talal\"}], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"a stunning twist\", \"from\": 648, \"to\": 664}, {\"ngram\": \"Kipyegon\", \"from\": 683, \"to\": 691}, {\"ngram\": \"the silver medal\", \"from\": 708, \"to\": 724}, {\"ngram\": \"a successful appeal\", \"from\": 754, \"to\": 773}, {\"ngram\": \"the decision\", \"from\": 782, \"to\": 794}, {\"ngram\": \"the bronze\", \"from\": 804, \"to\": 814}, {\"ngram\": \"Battocletti\", \"from\": 843, \"to\": 854}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Follow Metro.co.uk's live blog for updates from the Paris Olympics 2024 Replays of the controversial incident appeared to show Ethiopia's Tsegay cutting in front of Kipyegon and the Kenyan responded by taking a hold of her rival's arm - momentarily throwing her off balance.\", \"from\": 857, \"to\": 1132, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 985, \"end\": 993, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Ethiopia\", \"score\": 0.9996327367339226, \"rank\": 0.0003673949937708097, \"text\": \"Ethiopia\", \"types\": [\"Q6256\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Ethiopia\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Ethiopia\"}], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"Follow Metro.co.uk's live blog\", \"from\": 857, \"to\": 887}, {\"ngram\": \"updates\", \"from\": 892, \"to\": 899}, {\"ngram\": \"the Paris Olympics\", \"from\": 905, \"to\": 923}, {\"ngram\": \"2024 Replays\", \"from\": 924, \"to\": 936}, {\"ngram\": \"the controversial incident\", \"from\": 940, \"to\": 966}, {\"ngram\": \"front\", \"from\": 1013, \"to\": 1018}, {\"ngram\": \"Kipyegon\", \"from\": 1022, \"to\": 1030}, {\"ngram\": \"the Kenyan\", \"from\": 1035, \"to\": 1045}, {\"ngram\": \"a hold\", \"from\": 1066, \"to\": 1072}, {\"ngram\": \"balance\", \"from\": 1123, \"to\": 1130}]}, {\"sentence\": \"And while BBC pundit Radcliffe, a three-time London Marathon winner, felt Kipyegon was reckless in grabbing Tsegay's arm during their tussle, she predicted there would be a counter-protest from Kenya.\", \"from\": 1134, \"to\": 1334, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 1144, \"end\": 1147, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/BBC_Sport\", \"score\": 0.6112403563959943, \"rank\": 0.6355221420505363, \"text\": \"BBC\", \"types\": [\"Q4830453\", \"Q43229\", \"Q24229398\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/BBC_Sport\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/BBC_Sport\"}, {\"begin\": 1155, \"end\": 1164, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Daniel_Radcliffe\", \"score\": 0.9886432089628481, \"rank\": 0.011483963727844446, \"text\": \"Radcliffe\", \"types\": [\"Q729\", \"Q5\", \"Q215627\", \"Q19088\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Daniel_Radcliffe\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Daniel_Radcliffe\"}, {\"begin\": 1179, \"end\": 1194, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/London_Marathon\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 1.0102277034403635e-21, \"text\": \"London Marathon\", \"types\": [], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/London_Marathon\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/London_Marathon\"}, {\"begin\": 1328, \"end\": 1333, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Kenya\", \"score\": 0.9999889309286655, \"rank\": 1.1069191083659907e-05, \"text\": \"Kenya\", \"types\": [\"Q6256\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Kenya\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Kenya\"}], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"Kipyegon\", \"from\": 1208, \"to\": 1216}, {\"ngram\": \"Tsegay's arm\", \"from\": 1242, \"to\": 1254}, {\"ngram\": \"their tussle\", \"from\": 1262, \"to\": 1274}, {\"ngram\": \"a counter\", \"from\": 1305, \"to\": 1314}, {\"ngram\": \"protest\", \"from\": 1315, \"to\": 1322}]}, {\"sentence\": \"'Kipyegon pushed her out first, that's what she's disqualified for.\", \"from\": 1336, \"to\": 1403, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"Kipyegon\", \"from\": 1337, \"to\": 1345}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Tsegay did cut in too quickly but only after Faith had tried to push her out wide,' former British Olympian Radcliffe said on BBC Sport shortly after the race.\", \"from\": 1404, \"to\": 1563, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 1495, \"end\": 1502, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/British_Boxing_Board_of_Control\", \"score\": 0.9003209420741812, \"rank\": 0.10991331640379406, \"text\": \"British\", \"types\": [], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/British_Boxing_Board_of_Control\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/British_Boxing_Board_of_Control\"}, {\"begin\": 1503, \"end\": 1511, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Olympic_Games\", \"score\": 0.9999999893343557, \"rank\": 1.0665686130729509e-08, \"text\": \"Olympian\", \"types\": [], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Olympic_Games\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Olympic_Games\"}, {\"begin\": 1512, \"end\": 1521, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Daniel_Radcliffe\", \"score\": 0.9886432089628481, \"rank\": 0.011483963727844446, \"text\": \"Radcliffe\", \"types\": [\"Q729\", \"Q5\", \"Q215627\", \"Q19088\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Daniel_Radcliffe\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Daniel_Radcliffe\"}, {\"begin\": 1530, \"end\": 1539, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/BBC_Sport\", \"score\": 0.9999782497835238, \"rank\": 1.8884025546759845e-05, \"text\": \"BBC Sport\", \"types\": [\"Q4830453\", \"Q43229\", \"Q24229398\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/BBC_Sport\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/BBC_Sport\"}], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"Tsegay\", \"from\": 1404, \"to\": 1410}, {\"ngram\": \"Faith\", \"from\": 1449, \"to\": 1454}, {\"ngram\": \"the race\", \"from\": 1554, \"to\": 1562}]}, {\"sentence\": \"'I would not be surprised if there is another counter-protest because you can not grab hold of someone's arm and tell them to stay out.\", \"from\": 1565, \"to\": 1700, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"another counter\", \"from\": 1603, \"to\": 1618}, {\"ngram\": \"protest\", \"from\": 1619, \"to\": 1626}, {\"ngram\": \"hold\", \"from\": 1652, \"to\": 1656}, {\"ngram\": \"someone's arm\", \"from\": 1660, \"to\": 1673}]}, {\"sentence\": \"'You can warn with your hand, people will do that when you can feel someone's going to cut in.\", \"from\": 1702, \"to\": 1796, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"your hand\", \"from\": 1721, \"to\": 1730}, {\"ngram\": \"people\", \"from\": 1732, \"to\": 1738}, {\"ngram\": \"someone\", \"from\": 1770, \"to\": 1777}]}, {\"sentence\": \"'You can put your hand out and just warm them - but you can not grab hold of their arm and physically move them.'\", \"from\": 1798, \"to\": 1911, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"your hand\", \"from\": 1811, \"to\": 1820}, {\"ngram\": \"hold\", \"from\": 1867, \"to\": 1871}, {\"ngram\": \"their arm\", \"from\": 1875, \"to\": 1884}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Radcliffe argued that Kipyegon's move was unnecessary and felt the Kenyan took it 'a little bit too far' in her coming together with Tsegay.\", \"from\": 1913, \"to\": 2053, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 1913, \"end\": 1922, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Daniel_Radcliffe\", \"score\": 0.9886432089628481, \"rank\": 0.011483963727844446, \"text\": \"Radcliffe\", \"types\": [\"Q729\", \"Q5\", \"Q215627\", \"Q19088\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Daniel_Radcliffe\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Daniel_Radcliffe\"}], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"Kipyegon's move\", \"from\": 1935, \"to\": 1950}, {\"ngram\": \"the Kenyan\", \"from\": 1976, \"to\": 1986}, {\"ngram\": \"Tsegay\", \"from\": 2046, \"to\": 2052}]}, {\"sentence\": \"'You almost need to [push other athletes] from a safety point of view because if you are going to hit the track, that's far more devastating and dangerous for the race,' she added.\", \"from\": 2055, \"to\": 2235, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"other athletes\", \"from\": 2081, \"to\": 2095}, {\"ngram\": \"a safety point\", \"from\": 2102, \"to\": 2116}, {\"ngram\": \"view\", \"from\": 2120, \"to\": 2124}, {\"ngram\": \"the track\", \"from\": 2157, \"to\": 2166}, {\"ngram\": \"the race\", \"from\": 2214, \"to\": 2222}]}, {\"sentence\": \"'So be able to warn someone, \\\"Hey, you are stepping into my space, this is my space and my stride needs to go there.\", \"from\": 2237, \"to\": 2353, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"someone\", \"from\": 2257, \"to\": 2264}, {\"ngram\": \"my space\", \"from\": 2294, \"to\": 2302}, {\"ngram\": \"my space\", \"from\": 2312, \"to\": 2320}, {\"ngram\": \"my stride\", \"from\": 2325, \"to\": 2334}]}, {\"sentence\": \"You are not going there\\\", you are allowed to do that.\", \"from\": 2354, \"to\": 2407, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"'You are allowed to sometimes get away with accidentally grabbing someone if you are actually falling.\", \"from\": 2409, \"to\": 2511, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"someone\", \"from\": 2475, \"to\": 2482}]}, {\"sentence\": \"But to actually grab hold of their arm and move them wide\\u2026 I think that's why the DQ has gone in.'\", \"from\": 2512, \"to\": 2610, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 2594, \"end\": 2596, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/White_dwarf\", \"score\": 0.9999999016808991, \"rank\": 9.83187666402937e-08, \"text\": \"DQ\", \"types\": [], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/White_dwarf\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/White_dwarf\"}], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"hold\", \"from\": 2533, \"to\": 2537}, {\"ngram\": \"their arm\", \"from\": 2541, \"to\": 2550}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Radcliffe added: 'It's a real shame because it did not need to be done.\", \"from\": 2612, \"to\": 2683, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 2612, \"end\": 2621, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Daniel_Radcliffe\", \"score\": 0.9886432089628481, \"rank\": 0.011483963727844446, \"text\": \"Radcliffe\", \"types\": [\"Q729\", \"Q5\", \"Q215627\", \"Q19088\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Daniel_Radcliffe\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Daniel_Radcliffe\"}], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"a real shame\", \"from\": 2635, \"to\": 2647}]}, {\"sentence\": \"She could have responded by accelerating, by just putting out her hand.\", \"from\": 2684, \"to\": 2755, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"her hand\", \"from\": 2746, \"to\": 2754}]}, {\"sentence\": \"'But instead, she's gone a little bit too far and then Tsegay has responded by cutting back in and perhaps burned a little bit of her nervous adrenaline that was ready to go over that final 800m or so and that's later cost her dearly in the race.\", \"from\": 2757, \"to\": 3003, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"Tsegay\", \"from\": 2812, \"to\": 2818}, {\"ngram\": \"a little bit\", \"from\": 2871, \"to\": 2883}, {\"ngram\": \"her nervous adrenaline\", \"from\": 2887, \"to\": 2909}, {\"ngram\": \"that final 800m\", \"from\": 2936, \"to\": 2951}, {\"ngram\": \"the race\", \"from\": 2994, \"to\": 3002}]}, {\"sentence\": \"'The good thing that we can say is that we can say that the actual Olympic champion [Chebet], who ran a phenomenal race, you can absolutely applaud the way she did that.\", \"from\": 3005, \"to\": 3174, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"The good thing\", \"from\": 3006, \"to\": 3020}, {\"ngram\": \"Chebet\", \"from\": 3090, \"to\": 3096}, {\"ngram\": \"a phenomenal race\", \"from\": 3107, \"to\": 3124}]}, {\"sentence\": \"She was not involved in any way and managed to stay clear of it and nobody went down.'\", \"from\": 3175, \"to\": 3261, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"any way\", \"from\": 3199, \"to\": 3206}, {\"ngram\": \"nobody\", \"from\": 3243, \"to\": 3249}]}, {\"sentence\": \"After the disqualification was overturned, Hassan admitted she 'did not really feel like' she deserved to win the silver medal over Kipyegon.\", \"from\": 3263, \"to\": 3404, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 3306, \"end\": 3312, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Prince_Hassan_bin_Talal\", \"score\": 0.7369344478807932, \"rank\": 0.3569575148556968, \"text\": \"Hassan\", \"types\": [\"Q729\", \"Q5\", \"Q215627\", \"Q19088\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Prince_Hassan_bin_Talal\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Prince_Hassan_bin_Talal\"}], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"the disqualification\", \"from\": 3269, \"to\": 3289}, {\"ngram\": \"the silver medal\", \"from\": 3373, \"to\": 3389}, {\"ngram\": \"Kipyegon\", \"from\": 3395, \"to\": 3403}]}, {\"sentence\": \"'I am really happy that Faith gets her medal back.\", \"from\": 3406, \"to\": 3456, \"entities\": []